#: ../../V/velveeta.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Usenet: by analogy with :ref:`spam`\\. The trade name Velveeta is attached "
"in the U.S. to a particularly nasty processed-cheese spread.] Also knows as "
":ref:`ECP`\\; a message that is excessively cross-posted, as opposed to "
":ref:`spam` which is too frequently posted. This term is widely recognized "
"but not commonly used; most people refer to both kinds of abuse as spam. "
"Compare :ref:`jello`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Usenet: \\ :ref:`spam`\\ "
"との類推から。商標名Velveetaは米国で、とりわけ質の悪いプロセスチーズスプレッドに付けられている] \\ :ref:`ECP`\\ "
"としても知られる。過度にクロスポストされるメッセージで、頻繁すぎる頻度で投稿される\\ :ref:`spam`\\ "
"とは対照的なもの。この用語は広く認知されているが、一般的には使われない。ほとんどの人は両種の濫用をspamと呼ぶ。\\ :ref:`jello`\\ "
"と比較せよ。"
